*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.swf binary
*.svgz binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.bz2 binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.obj binary
*.lib binary
*.class binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
*.dmg binary
*.iso binary
*.img binary
